     fhir:status [ fhir:v "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p><b>Generated Narrative: PlanDefinition</b><a name=\"NoTherapeuticAnticoagulationICUCOVID19NoIndicationPlan\"> </a><a name=\"hcNoTherapeuticAnticoagulationICUCOVID19NoIndicationPlan\"> </a></p><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Resource PlanDefinition &quot;NoTherapeuticAnticoagulationICUCOVID19NoIndicationPlan&quot; </p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profile: <a href=\"file:///github/workspace/output/StructureDefinition-recommendation-plan.html\">Recommendation Plan</a></p></div><p><b>knowledgeCapability</b>: computable</p><p><b>knowledgeRepresentationLevel</b>: structured</p><p><b>partOf</b>: <a href=\"PlanDefinition-RecCollectionNoTherapeuticAnticoagNoIndicationICUCOVID19.html\">Anticoagulation Plan for Population: ICU COVID-19 Patients with No Specific Indication</a></p><blockquote><p><b>Action Combination Method</b></p><blockquote><p><b>url</b></p><code>method</code></blockquote><p><b>value</b>: All <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"file:///github/workspace/output/CodeSystem-cs-action-combination-method.html\">Action Combination Method</a>#all)</span></p></blockquote><p><b>url</b>: <code>https://www.netzwerk-universitaetsmedizin.de/fhir/codex-celida/guideline/covid19-inpatient-therapy/intervention-plan/no-therapeutic-anticoagulation</code></p><p><b>identifier</b>: TherapeuticAnticoagulationICUCOVID19NoIndication</p><p><b>version</b>: 7.0</p><p><b>name</b>: Anticoagulation_Plan_No_Specific_Indication</p><p><b>title</b>: Anticoagulation Plan for hospitalized intensive-care COVID-19 patients with no specific indication</p><p><b>type</b>: ECA Rule <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.5.0/CodeSystem-plan-definition-type.html\">PlanDefinitionType</a>#eca-rule)</span></p><p><b>status</b>: active</p><p><b>experimental</b>: true</p><p><b>subject</b>: <a href=\"EvidenceVariable-PopHospitalisedICUCOVID19Patients.html\">Hospitalised COVID-19 patients, treated on ICU, without thrombembolic complication</a></p><p><b>date</b>: 2022-02</p><p><b>publisher</b>: NUM CODEX+ CELIDA</p><p><b>description</b>: In intensive care patients without a specific indication (e.g. pulmonary embolism), therapeutic anticoagulation should not be given.</p><blockquote><p><b>goal</b></p><blockquote><p><b>id</b></p>aPTT-goal</blockquote><p><b>category</b>: Lab findings surveillance (regime/therapy) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#410394004)</span></p><p><b>description</b>: aPTT value should not be &gt; 50 sec. <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> ()</span></p><h3>Targets</h3><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td style=\"display: none\">-</td><td><b>Measure</b></td><td><b>Detail[x]</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"display: none\">*</td><td>aPTT in Blood by Coagulation assay <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://loinc.org/\">LOINC</a>#3173-2)</span></td><td>50-? sec</td></tr></table></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>code</b>: Administration of substance (procedure) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#432102000)</span></p><p><b>goalId</b>: aPTT-goal</p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-NoTherapeuticAnticoagulationWUFH.html\">No Therapeutic Anticoagulation Treatment with UFH</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>code</b>: Administration of substance (procedure) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#432102000)</span></p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-NoTherapeuticAnticoagulationWDalteparin1xd.html\">No Therapeutic Anticoagulation Treatment with Dalteparin</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>code</b>: Administration of substance (procedure) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#432102000)</span></p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-NoTherapeuticAnticoagulationWDalteparin2xd.html\">No Therapeutic Anticoagulation Treatment with Dalteparin</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>code</b>: Administration of substance (procedure) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#432102000)</span></p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-NoTherapeuticAnticoagulationWDalteparinTable.html\">No Therapeutic Anticoagulation Treatment with Dalteparin</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>code</b>: Administration of substance (procedure) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#432102000)</span></p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-NoTherapeuticAnticoagulationWNadroparin.html\">No Therapeutic Anticoagulation Treatment with Nadroparin</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>action</b></p><p><b>code</b>: Administration of substance (procedure) <span style=\"background: LightGoldenRodYellow; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid khaki\"> (<a href=\"https://browser.ihtsdotools.org/\">SNOMED CT</a>#432102000)</span></p><p><b>definition</b>: <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-NoTherapeuticAnticoagulationWEnoxaparin1xd.html\">No Therapeutic Anticoagulation Treatment with En